1. The project uses Yarn as its package manager.
2. Lerna is employed to manage the monorepo.
3. Use snake_case naming convention for all function and variable names.
4. For styles in the docs folder, use Tailwind CSS consistently, only write direct CSS when Tailwind cannot handle the requirements.
5. Always check the current directory, ensure to cd to the correct path before executing commands or creating files.
6. Every time opening a terminal, execute a cd command first to ensure entering the correct directory, using the format "cd && command".

